---
title: Bruschetta Balsamic-Glazed Salmon with Parmesan Roasted Potatoes
description: We've taken the classic Italian antipasto and made it a meal for two with succulent salmon and Parmesan roasted potato wedges. A final drizzle of balsamic glaze and you're all set for date night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/saumon-au-glacage-balsamique-et-a-la-bruschetta-7fc8ccc8.jpg
